Package: rodev
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: Helper for rOpenSci Package Developpers
Description: Provides helpers for rOpenSci package developpers,
  mostly helping with metadata management (badges, DESCRIPTION)
  and GitHub infrastructure (GitHub issue and PR templates).
